{"tid":891133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殺人犯出獄找不到女友　憤而自宮大失血嚇壞母親","createTime":"2018-11-06T00:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T10:50:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"644318802fd0d8319081ccc15115aa2f5daed5c9","tid":891133,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"泰國一名41歲男子佩特努(Reawat Petnui)曾是殺人犯，現已出獄在家，但他為交不到女友所苦，竟然在家中憤而自宮。母親發現他倒在血泊中的模樣，整個人被嚇壞。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，佩特努在多年前犯下殺人案，當時他在吸食毒品過後產生幻覺，並殺害2名友人，佩特努最後被判12年徒刑，而他在服刑10年之後獲假釋出獄。佩特努出獄後一直待在家中，幫助家人照顧橡膠園。但家人指出，佩特努出獄後想要找女友，跟多位女生約會都沒有結果，最近他想追一名7-11超商女孩，但對方告訴他「我有老公了」，頓時間佩特努晴天霹靂，完全無法接受這個事實。<br />\n據悉佩特努失戀後相當難過，把自己關在房間中。就在周日早上11點多，佩特努的71歲母親桑布姆(Somboon)嘗試叫他，但佩特努沒有回應，之後桑布姆直接進門，發現佩特努整個人倒在血泊中，下體大失血。<br />\n佩特努隨後被送醫，目前他狀況穩定，正在治療與復原中。桑布姆說：「我兒子很乖的，還曾在曼谷念大學，但後來他染毒產生幻覺，在一場打鬥中殺了兩人。」桑布姆也說，佩特努出獄後幾乎都待在家裡，且鮮少與外人說話，但他盡量讓自己回歸正常社會生活，他現在最愛的活動，就是到超商購物，更進一步想要追那名超商女孩，卻被拒絕。佩特努失戀後，意志變得極度消沉，最後選擇在房內自宮。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_d86718eb0038868d60150a0f5f6cb32f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_d86718eb0038868d60150a0f5f6cb32f.jpg&h=2d518a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_67a4e4bf73b607a54d0a249a7c4707c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_67a4e4bf73b607a54d0a249a7c4707c6.jpg&h=76eb985c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_1bd3aaeea9290dc8709f355382334f24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_1bd3aaeea9290dc8709f355382334f24.jpg&h=03aafa8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf318ce199c6463aac4d0d7d19251be58442a39","tid":891133,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:58:27.000Z","msg":"成排骨"},{"pid":"2a88ae5effa77b032374a405f56eec23e61bffc8","tid":891133,"uid":74911,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:03:10.000Z","msg":"我兒子很乖 只殺了兩個人<br />\n佢老母傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfc521966271203c1ea27d8d44f24dec59c44b4","tid":891133,"uid":2567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子啊.jpg"},{"pid":"d643e98c54b9ff368e746c6706f50347b2a012b5","tid":891133,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a88ae5effa77b032374a405f56eec23e61bffc8","tid":891133,"uid":74911,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:03:10.000Z","msg":"我兒子很乖 只殺了兩個人<br />\n佢老母傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"我個仔好乖佢只係強姦左幾十個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌有無咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea76402706ebb96956eaad9921486089891b33b4","tid":891133,"uid":58851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a88ae5effa77b032374a405f56eec23e61bffc8","tid":891133,"uid":74911,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:03:10.000Z","msg":"我兒子很乖 只殺了兩個人<br />\n佢老母傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"香港唔單止吸毒個班係咁諗<br />\n就連醉駕殺人個班都係咁諗, 包括法官"},{"pid":"36a78e200a9619e7175347d3eeb90bf6c5edf85c","tid":891133,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abfc521966271203c1ea27d8d44f24dec59c44b4","tid":891133,"uid":2567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子啊.jpg"}